d method as an\nindicator for a player without the ball to create a scoring chance for\nteammates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jun 2022 03:58:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Jul 2022 07:10:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 00:25:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-28"}
