ater's\nelectromagnetic wave energy. This paper is, to authors' best knowledge, the\nfirst observation of this kind of \"self-absorption\" measured from the\ntransionospheric signal path from a powerful radio source on the ground to the\nsatellite-borne receiver.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jun 2022 06:37:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
