mprehensive ablation studies to demonstrate the advantages and effectiveness\nof core modules of our method. In addition, we apply CClusnet-Inseg to\nmulti-object tracking for animal monitoring, and the predicted object center\nthat is a conjunct output could serve as an occlusion-resistant representation\nof the location of an object.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jun 2022 08:43:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2023 04:11:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 08:19:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
